This package contains original package code and bundled tokenizer assets under a
mixed-license distribution.

Bundled tokenizer asset origins:
- moonshotai/Kimi-K2-Instruct tokenizer snapshot: upstream Modified MIT License
  with a "Kimi K2" UI attribution condition.
- moonshotai/Kimi-K2-Thinking tokenizer snapshot: upstream Modified MIT License
  with a "Kimi K2" UI attribution condition.
- moonshotai/Moonlight-16B-A3B tokenizer snapshot: the upstream model card
  README front matter declares `license: mit`.
- moonshotai/Kimi-Dev-72B tokenizer snapshot: upstream LICENSE.md states
  "Subject to the Qwen LICENSE AGREEMENT, Kimi-Dev-72B is under MIT license."

Supported aliases such as Kimi-K2-Base, Kimi-K2-Instruct-0905,
Kimi-Linear-48B-A3B-Base, Kimi-Linear-48B-A3B-Instruct, and
Moonlight-16B-A3B-Instruct are mapped to the bundled canonical snapshots above
and are not shipped as separate tokenizer assets in this package.

You must comply with the terms that apply to the bundled asset you redistribute.

